data.description: Nestled in the sought-after Newaukum Village neighborhood, this 3-bedroom, 2-bath gem is a haven of comfort and convenience. Enjoy the charm of no HOA restrictions in the esteemed Chehalis School District. Proximity to a golf course and easy access to I5 make recreation and commuting a breeze. Recent upgrades include new paint in parts of the home, newer flooring throughout, and updated outlets. The kitchen featuring a gas stove. With a 2-car garage and thoughtful improvements, this residence seamlessly combines practicality with style. Embrace the warmth of a home that captures the essence of modern living. Your ideal lifestyle awaits—schedule a viewing today!
